snippet.title: SpongeBob Lights, Camera, Pants! [PC] - Longplay (100%) [4K]
snippet.description:
SpongeBob SquarePants: Lights, Camera, Pants! (LCP) [2005]
PC / Windows
100% Longplay
4:3 Aspect Ratio
4K (UHD) [2880p x 2160p] 60fps

Timestamps

Levels:
1. Eastern Bikini Bottom - 1:04
2. Northern Bikini Bottom - 35:50
3. Western Bikini Bottom - 1:15:55
4. Southern Bikini Bottom - 1:46:15
5. The New Adventures of Mermaidman and Barnacleboy - 2:07:50
6. All Minigames - 2:18:20

Other
100% / Everything Unlocked - 2:06:25
Credits - 2:37:16


•This is a complete 100% Walkthrough of "SpongeBob SquarePants: Lights, Camera, Pants!" for the PC/Windows
•This Longplay is all the parts of my Walkthrough of this game put together in one video. I didn't redo this one because my walkthrough was already perfect concerning both, Gameplay Quality and Video Quality, so there was nothing else I could have added or done better if I replayed this game.
•In this Longplay I will unlock all actors and collect all props in each Level, I click on mainly all objects if it isn't too time consuming and would become boring otherwise (e.g. all the weapons in the Mermalair)
• This is one of our beloved Childhood Games and very nostalgic for some.

•4K UHD - Resolution with consistent 60fps and smooth Gameplay. This video is supposed to give you the best possible experience of everything the game has to offer.
•This game normally only runs in 480p and 15fps. I upscaled it to 4K and 60fps using dgVoodoo 2. I stretched the picture to 16:9 Aspect Ratio, I wasn't sure whether to do so or not, my brother said it was better so I did that.

Be sure to Subscribe for more high quality SpongeBob Video Game content!
